
// The code executes a workflow action named "markdown2html" by calling the slot [magic.workflows.actions.execute]. It specifies the filename of the action and passes in arguments, where the [markdown] argument is set to the result of an expression that retrieves and HTML encodes the content from a specific node path.
execute:magic.workflows.actions.execute
   name:markdown2html
   filename:/misc/workflows/actions/misc/markdown2html.hl
   arguments
      markdown:x:--/execute/=html-encode-body/*/content
